longBusinessSummary: Kwan's International Co., Ltd. operates in the film and television cultural industry. The company engages in the wholesale and sale of cultural and educational, musical instruments, and recreational products; general advertising services; publishing of magazines, books, and audiobooks; film production and distribution; arts and cultural services; performing of arts activities; and broadcasting of video program tape. It is also involved in the production of concerts and music lyrics; planning, outsourcing, and distribution of music tapes, records, and laser films; production and trading of music video shooting; import and export trade; and provision of artist training course, press conferences, and events, as well as 3D advertising and ads printing. The company was formerly known as Victory Circuit Co., Ltd. and changed its name to Kwan's International Co., Ltd. in August 2017. Kwan's International Co., Ltd. was founded in 1978 and is based in Taipei, Taiwan.
